org.opentcs.access.queries

Annotation Type Availability

  • Deprecated. 
    Instead of queries, explicit service calls should be used.

    @Documented
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
 @Deprecated
 @ScheduledApiChange(when="5.0")
public @interface Availability
    Indicates in which kernel states the annotated query is available.
    See Also:
    Kernel.State, Kernel.getState()
